a:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Figma AI is best suited for UI/UX designers, design teams, product teams, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Visme, meanwhile, shines for marketers, educators, business professionals, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2012, Figma AI describes itself as \"Professional UI design tool with AI-powered design assistance features.\" Visme, established in 2013, positions itself as \"Design platform for creating presentations, infographics, and visual content.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
b:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Figma AI** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (9.0 vs 7.0), more features (9 vs 8), availability of a free plan. However, this does not mean Visme is a poor choice — far from it. Visme excels in its own right, particularly for marketers and educators.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value industry-standard ui design tool, go with Figma AI. If excellent for data visualization matters more to you, Visme is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
